						<summary>

						<p>Slab in front of the Veṇugōpālasvāmin temple.</p>						

						<p>Sadāśiva, 1554 A.D.</p>						

						<p>This is dated <hi rend="bold">Śaka 147[2], Sādhāraṇa, Mārgaśira ba. 12</hi> corresponding to <hi rend="bold">1550 A.D. December 5, Friday.</hi></p>						

						<p>Damaged. Seems to record the remission of tax on the barbers in the time of Pina Aubhaḷayyadēva Mahārāja of Naṅdyāla.</p>						

						</summary>
